Round 3: tightened the eval_error persistence rule in 03 §4.4.

On eval_error submissions (both intermediate and the retry-exhausted terminal case), the orchestrator MUST NOT write metrics or artifacts_uri onto the trial. Any submission-carried values are discarded. An evaluator that wants to retain diagnostic artifacts from a failed attempt may reference them in the task.failed event (channel to be defined in 05-event-protocol.md).

This keeps the trial canonical: it either carries a success/error evaluation's outputs, or nothing.

Please re-read spec/v0/03-roles.md §4.4 and confirm whether anything else blocks merge.
